Package: indicator-script-runner
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python3:Depends}, gir1.2-appindicator3-0.1, libnotify-bin, python3-gi
Description: Run a terminal command or script from a GUI front-end.
 Allows the user to specify a terminal command or script with parameters
 and use the mouse (or keyboard shortcut) to execute the command/script
 rather than opening a terminal and type out (or up arrow or grep history)
 the command.